title: Stop #12 of 2006/2007 PBRJ Tour - Mount Seymour, BC, Canada
description: The 12th stop on the 2006/07 PBRJ tour went down on the summit of Vancouver's Mount Seymour on Saturday March 31st. Click the movie to check out all the action. Music by Die Hunns.
